{"tid":567823,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"【業界良心】第 2 代 RYZEN 桌上型 CPU 將沿用錫焊散熱","createTime":"2018-02-21T08:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T11:52:01.000Z","uid":1886,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a864d991e454480a31114bdd34612df00a9bd855","tid":567823,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T08:01:17.000Z","msg":"第 2 代 AMD Ryzen 桌上型 CPU 將於今年 4 月推出，雖然其 Zen+ 架構只為 Ryzen 5 1600 、 Ryzen 7 1800X 等第一代「 Summit Ridge 」的改良版，不會有太大的變化或功能新增，但相信不少 AMD 粉絲及想「轉會」的用戶都對此系列滿心期待。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/AMD-2nd-Generation-Ryzen-Processors-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2FAMD-2nd-Generation-Ryzen-Processors-1.jpg&h=bd6faa83&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\nAMD 的技術人員 Robert Hallock 用官方的帳號，在 Reddit 討論區確認第 2 代 Ryzen CPU 亦將使用錫焊散熱。用戶購買新一代 CPU 後，毋需開蓋更換芯片與 IHS 之間的散熱材質，已經能夠獲得不錯的散熱效果，CPU 温度更低，就可持續高效能，超頻表現亦更佳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/02/21/第2代ryzen桌電級cpu將沿用錫焊散熱/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2F2018%2F02%2F21%2F%E7%AC%AC2%E4%BB%A3ryzen%E6%A1%8C%E9%9B%BB%E7%B4%9Acpu%E5%B0%87%E6%B2%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%8C%AB%E7%84%8A%E6%95%A3%E7%86%B1%2F&d=Px4FN%2BDPswkdiCZyJZdSqaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=32381d03\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/2018/02/21/第2代ryzen桌電級cpu將沿用錫焊散熱/</a>"},{"pid":"823b05986a081de3f885001e48b84955d91c55df","tid":567823,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T08:07:05.000Z","msg":"AMD 在 Ryzen 2000 系列沿用錫焊散熱，確實反映出企業良心，不像「牙膏廠」那樣，近萬元的 i9 都依然使用矽脂。不過並非所有 AMD 的新 CPU 都會用錫焊，例如最近新推出的 Ryzen 5 2400G 和 Ryzen 3 2200G APU 就採用了矽脂，應該是為了成本以及 APU 廉宜售價的考量。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.pcmarket.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/AMD-Ryzen-5-2400G-IHS-v2_-872x579.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pcmarket.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2FAMD-Ryzen-5-2400G-IHS-v2_-872x579.jpg&h=3e288c34&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"da3d4db887730fb01d13ca055c0e68e7e594b9a0","tid":567823,"uid":69778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://techreport.com/r.x/2017_03_31_In_the_lab_AMD_s_Ryzen_5_1600X_and_Ryzen_5_1500X_CPUs/wraithspire.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechreport.com%2Fr.x%2F2017_03_31_In_the_lab_AMD_s_Ryzen_5_1600X_and_Ryzen_5_1500X_CPUs%2Fwraithspire.jpg&h=18177ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nstock cooler 都高質過intel"},{"pid":"e59988a0baf6ae7798215209de82290205b4cc05","tid":567823,"uid":154264,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:24:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"173ac7eb37d903d19ecd96cb73de9005b74c14c1","tid":567823,"uid":113626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:25:56.000Z","msg":"ryzen 1600 4月賣出去仲有幾銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要換新u了"},{"pid":"3ab4ed71e59418180cf3fc775bfc886e7994bd0f","tid":567823,"uid":26611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:56:43.000Z","msg":"AMD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dacac804c7f77692b59e7eb88eb2168db31ce58","tid":567823,"uid":139020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"173ac7eb37d903d19ecd96cb73de9005b74c14c1","tid":567823,"uid":113626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T09:25:56.000Z","msg":"ryzen 1600 4月賣出去仲有幾銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要換新u了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}